Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于凌晨发生于阿留多人街头的炸弹恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦警察怀疑这次恐怖事件可能是针对前来阿留多人街进行慰问的\N同盟总领事兼和平特使贝·凯拉布·贝拉氏的暗杀行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而持续调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  讨厌  社会动乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问题已经很严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能给同盟侵略中立地区的口实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们联邦在银河均等的势力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在围绕着贝利奥斯塔中立地区的所有权互相对立
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是恐怖事件发生前监视摄像头拍到的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是乌鲁卡人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能停留时间还有两天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有得到更长的许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您同意我参加调查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于炸弹恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人街一带被毁得一片狼藉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此现场还未能确认贝·凯拉布·贝拉氏的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生存的可能性近乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潘戈里安牛奶苏打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了缓和中立地区的紧张气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔乌吉市市政官对同盟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12帕尔  先付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带同族很少见啊   多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  博伊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多的女人又臭又讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  那么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我技术很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咯吱  咯吱  咯吱  咯吱  咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很熟练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你昨天在阿留多街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你知道的可真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你为什么会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这可不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不要停  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉我就不帮你做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一般做生意的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这把枪是禁止一般人持有的贝诺加型光线枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里把你作为现行犯逮捕要更省事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊  我们可是有营业执照的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到这里应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是携带违法枪支的现行犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你  还没回答我的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接着来享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕多拉  救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你下手还是不够狠呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不能杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放开  蛮力女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才快给我住手  分尸狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  毕多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我大忙了  尼姆凯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时如果不是神祇官介入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌疑犯就能抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祇官直属于奥之院  不受司法管制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加上她还是特察官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特撮片监督？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是指获得杀人许可的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而她介入了这次的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来奥之院对此事有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样  现在又回到起点了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,数小时前  自称新秩序革命战线的组织发表了犯罪声明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  联邦的诸位公仆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是还在浪费税金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好  我是新秩序革命战线的司令官金泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是金泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是在艾尔卡扎姆被你和奈丘拉抓住的金泽尔·豪瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是米拉托综合大学毕业的知识分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在行星艾翁上做着吃人的野蛮行径的凶恶恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半年前  从阿特拉的卫星监狱逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我们再次警告诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12小时后  给予那肮脏的同盟总领事馆制裁之锤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是仁慈的我想给诸位最后的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能满足我们的要求  可以取消这次正义行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  我们指定这两人来谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿  看着吧  她俩马上就要来谈判了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我吃发臭牢饭的那些母猫们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我饶不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对饶不了你们  那些臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖  乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  一直给我们资金援助的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能够理解我的革命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是大学里的好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的工作也是那位赞助者大人的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸毁同盟的领事馆对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来下你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的目标是那些计算机人类的老窝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那就是把奥之院…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然从大学出来的做事就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说这次的也是媲美反物质炸弹的烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机动公安部那边习惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个年纪了还在实际行动部队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你适合跑现场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  贝利奥斯塔中立地区好像集结了同盟的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会发展到战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在尽力阻止啊  唯吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  我们要尽快逮捕金泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为同族真是感到丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是金泽尔是个二流主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认为就凭他一个人能策划出这次的计划来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你发现什么了吗  斯凯尔兹奥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…说起来  那对搭档重新组合了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又是跟你这家伙合作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还包括金泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金泽尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能我们之间有缘分的红线连着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这人还会开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来自这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从懂事的时候开始  都是白奥林在照顾我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,育儿用机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  母亲的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们阿留多人的公墓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金泽尔  按照约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯以及另一人来谈判了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这情况原来也遇到过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾尔卡扎姆是一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没进步的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这惨状  活不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  嘿嘿  真是活该
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  阿留多人的小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被他看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  亲爱的  别杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在工作完成之前  把他关起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切  知道啦  随你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你就是赞助者大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你装死真是把我都吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凯拉布总领事殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了  金泽尔·豪瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,汝只要完成余的委托就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首都上空1万缪鲁的静止卫星轨道上漂浮的废弃电力卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把这卫星落到奥之院上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样让半径40缪鲁毁灭的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星下降开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在高度8千  进入角度70  误差修正25比塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按预定路线下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  该怎么做才好  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  现在停止也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一按这个卫星就会自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  开玩笑  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟的家伙们不懂幽默还真是没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  那个是控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以奥之院毁灭为信号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们舰队向中立地区的中心进军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以压倒的战力光复曾今失去的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为和平特使的余被联邦暗杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如有这个大义名分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的进攻就是正当的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了的和平特使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小男孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这小鬼  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把那东西还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老实呆着  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就把你生吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  你能办得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认命吧  金泽尔·豪瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然招来了搜查官  金泽尔这个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子的老巢里出现了本该死去的同盟总领事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金泽尔  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大学里我制造的杰作三重阿努比斯7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有匹敌重型战车的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别人说话要听完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的金泽尔  竟然让卫星坠落…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坠落地点分析完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是奥之院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没用  没用  没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它比你们调整型阿留多人更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看大学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你把我的话听完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  这个怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尼姆凯  快交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}距离目标还有60
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  那个要是坠落了  很多无辜的人会丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  大概50人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别听这女人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会死很多人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  我的甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  就差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您说的话我不太明白  神祇官殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「以奥之院毁灭为信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们舰队向中立地区的中心进军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以压倒的战力光复曾今失去的领土」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个公布出去的话  同盟就…啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊  神祇官出现在这里是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白  我们也省事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是本国同盟政府的意图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下充满勇气的行为将给我们双方带来利益
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,处世之道我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾之血为同盟正义的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政治了结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  竟会在这里  我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那只野狗在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是大学毕业的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金泽尔及其同伙被阿特拉的卫星收容所监禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟也接受凯拉布总领事因为恐怖分子而殉职的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤回指责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,避免了一触即发的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是所谓的政治了结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我失去知觉没法联络你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎么确定他们的老巢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这问题由我来回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来介绍  他是潜入搜查官…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡修·盖泽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是斯凯尔兹奥的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原来也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是秘密作战  请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是斯凯尔兹奥教官的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是你的同门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入调查的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的恐怖事件也可以防患于未然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不那么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法揭穿同盟的阴谋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是为了完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜牺牲无辜的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了拯救更多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了拯救更多的生命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  我不配说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说军方的工作人员也潜入了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了避免比尔盖巴的惨剧再次发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我们的女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  快点接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  家里有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  稍微离开了东京一会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没事的  明天回去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天见
